      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "MARRANZANO (9) returns to Rickie Alchin after campaigning in Queensland at the end of his juvenile season. Has not raced for four months but looks forward enough after a close second in a Menangle trial. Draws on the back row but won the only time he attempted this circuit and distance. A BUCK TEN (10) enjoys a big class drop off a NSW Derby heat last time out at Menangle. Hard to know where he gets to from this draw but he goes well at this circuit and distance, recording a win and two placings from three attempts. BILLS SWAN SONG (8) toughed out a last-start win by a head at Dubbo, giving him two wins and two placings from his last four starts. Draws on the back row but won the last time he started from there. INSIDE MAGIC (7) has been readied with two city trials so is worth keeping safe.",
